<p style="text-align: center;">Â <a href="http://www.faitsetcauses.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Signe-de-paix-blocage-Loto-Quebec_PLD_20120307_163.1000.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-3473" alt="Sans titre" src="http://www.faitsetcauses.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Signe-de-paix-blocage-Loto-Quebec_PLD_20120307_163.1000.jpg" width="600" height="402" /></a></p>
